\c 25
\s Gore resabata nereJubheri
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi pagomo reSinai achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri ugoti kwavari: Kana masvika munyika yandinokupai, nyika ichazorora, isabata kuna Jehovha\x + Eki. 23.10,11. 26.34,35. 2 Makor. 36.21.\x*.
\v 3 Makore matanhatu uchadzvara munda wako, uye makore matanhatu uchachekerera munda wako wemizambiringa nekuunganidza michero yayo.
\v 4 Asi mugore rechinomwe kuchava nesabata rekuzorora kwenyika, isabata kuna Jehovha; haungadzvari munda wako kana kuchekerera munda wako wemizambiringa\x + 25.11. 2 Madz. 19.29. Isa. 37.30.\x*.
\v 5 Haungakohwi magoko egoho rako, uye hamungaunganidzi zvibereko zvemunda wako wemizambiringa usina kuchekererwa; richava gore rekuzorora renyika.
\v 6 Zvino sabata renyika richava zvekudya zvenyu; zvako, nezvemuranda wako, nezvemurandakadzi wako, nezvemushandi wakahaiwa* wako, nezvemutorwa wako, vagere newe sevaeni;
\v 7 nezvezvipfuwo zvako, nezvemhuka dziri munyika yako; zvibereko zvadzo zvese zvichava zvekudya.
\p
\v 8 Zvino uchazviverengera masabata manomwe emakore, makore manomwe akapetwa kanomwe; kuti mazuva emasabata manomwe emakore ave kwauri makore makumi mana nemapfumbamwe.
\v 9 Ipapo uchapfuudza hwamanda yekurira kukuru mumwedzi wechinomwe nereshanu remwedzi; pazuva rechiyananiso muchapfuudza hwamanda panyika yose yekwenyu\x + 23.24,27.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino muchaita gore, regore remakumi mashanu dzvene, mugoparidza rusununguko panyika kuvagari vose vayo; richava jubheri kwamuri\x + Isa. 61.1. Jer. 34.8,15,17. Eze. 46.17. Isa. 61.2. 63.4. Ruk. 4.19.\x*; uye muchadzokera umwe neumwe kunhaka yake, uye muchadzokera umwe neumwe kudzinza rake\x + 25.13. 27.24. Num. 36.4.\x*.
\v 11 Gore regore remakumi mashanu richava jubheri kwamuri; musadzvara, uye musakohwa naro magoko\x + 25.5.\x*, uye musaunganidza naro zvemunda wemizambiringa usina kuchekererwa\x + 25.5.\x*.
\v 12 Nokuti ijubheri; richava dzvene kwamuri; muchadya zvibereko zvaro paminda\x + 25.6,7.\x*.
\v 13 Mugore iri rejubheri muchadzokera umwe neumwe kunhaka yake\x + 25.10.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino kana uchitengesa chinhu kune wekwako, kana kutenga muruoko rwewekwako, musamanikidzana\x + 25.17; 19.33.\x*.
\v 15 Zvichienderana neuwandu hwemakore shure kwejubheri uchatenga kune wekwako; zvichienderana neuwandu hwemakore ezvibereko achakutengesera\x + 27.18,23.\x*.
\v 16 Zvichienderana neuzhinji hwemakore achakwidza mutengo wazvo, uye zvichienderana neushoma hwemakore uchadzikisa mutengo wazvo; nokuti anokutengesera uwandu hwegoho.
\v 17 Naizvozvo musamanikidzana\x + 25.14.\x*, asi utye Mwari wako; nokuti ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu\x + 25.36,43; 19.14,32.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Naizvozvo itai zvimiso zvangu, nekuchengeta mitongo yangu, nekuzviita\x + 18.4,5.\x*, kuti mugare munyika makachengeteka\x + 25.19; 26.5. Det. 12.10. Map. 4.8. Eze. 34.25,28. Job. 11.18. Zvir. 1.33. Jer. 23.6.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino nyika ichabereka zvibereko zvayo, mugodya kusvika maguta, mugogaramo makachengeteka\x + 26.5. Det. 11.15. Jow. 2.19,26.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino kana muchiti: Tichadyei mugore rechinomwe\x + Mat. 6.25,31.\x*? Tarirai, hatidzvari kana kuunganidza zvibereko zvedu\x + 25.4,5.\x*;
\v 21 ipapo ndicharaira ropafadzo yangu pamusoro penyu mugore rechitanhatu, zvino richaita zvibereko zvemakore matatu\x + Eki. 16.29.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino muchadzvara mugore rerusere, mugodya\x + 2 Madz. 19.29.\x* pazvibereko zvitsaru, kusvika gore repfumbamwe; kusvika zvibereko zvaro zvichisvika, muchadya zvitsaru\x + Josh. 5.11,12. Rev. 26.10.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Nyika haitengeswi nekusingaperi, nokuti nyika ndeyangu\x + Det. 32.43. 2 Makor. 7.20. Map. 85.1. Jow. 2.18; 3.2.\x*; nokuti muri vatorwa nevagere sevaeni neni\x + 1 Makor. 29.15. Map. 39.12; 119.19. VaHeb. 11.13. 1 Pet. 1.17; 2.11.\x*.
\v 24 Zvino panyika yose yenhaka yenyu muchapa rudzikunuro rwenyika.
\p
\v 25 Kana umwe wako akava murombo, ndokutengesa \add zvimwe\add* panhaka yake, ipapo mudzikunuri\x + Rut. 2.20; 4.4,6.\x* ari pedo kuna iye akauya achadzikunura zvakatengeswa neumwe wake\x + Rut. 3.9,12. Jer. 32.7,8.\x*.
\v 26 Zvino kana munhu asina mudzikunuri, asi ruoko rwake rwuchisvikira, akawana zvinokwana rudzikunuro rwake;
\v 27 ipapo achaverenga makore ekutengeswa kwazvo, agodzosera muraudzo kumunhu waakaitengesera, adzokere kunhaka yake\x + 25.50,51,52.\x*.
\v 28 Asi kana ruoko rwake rusina kuwana zvakakwana kudzikunura kwaari, chakatengeswa chake chichava muruoko rwewakachitenga kusvika gore rejubheri; zvino pajubheri chichabuda, iye agodzokera kunhaka yake.
\p
\v 29 Zvino munhu, kana akatengesa imba yekugara muguta rine rusvingo, ipapo kodzero yerudzikunuro rwayo ichavapo kusvika pakupera kwegore rekutengeswa kwayo; kodzero yekuidzikunura ichavapo gore rese\x + 25.30. Gen. 24.55.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino kana isina kudzikunurwa mukati megore rakazara kwairi, ipapo imba iri muguta rine rusvingo ichasimbiswa nekusingaperi kune wakaitenga mumazera ake; haingabudi pajubheri.
\v 31 Asi dzimba dzemisha dzisina rusvingo kupoteredza dzichaverengwa semunda wenyika; dzichava rudzikunuro kwadziri, uye dzichabuda pajubheri.
\v 32 Maererano nemaguta eVaRevhi, dzimba dzemaguta enhaka yavo, kodzero yerudzikunuro yekusingaperi\x + Num. 35.2. Josh. 21.2,.\x* ichava kuVaRevhi.
\v 33 Zvino kana kune anodzikunura kuva Revhi, ipapo imba yakatengeswa neguta renhaka yake zvichabuda pajubheri; nokuti dzimba dzemaguta eVaRevhi inhaka yavo pakati pevana vaIsraeri\x + 25.28,30,31,41,54; 27.21.\x*.
\v 34 Asi munda wekumacheto kwemaguta avo haungatengeswi, nokuti inhaka yavo nekusingaperi\x + Num. 35.2. Josh. 21.11-42; 1 Makor. 6.55-81; 13.2. Mab. 4.36,37.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Zvino kana umwe wako akava murombo, neruoko rwake runodedera anewe, ipapo uchamutsigira, mutorwa kana mweni, kuti ararame pamwe newe\x + Det. 15.7,8. Map. 41.1; 112.5,9. Zvir. 14.31. 1 Joh. 3.17.\x*.
\v 36 Usatora mubereko kana zvibereko kwaari\x + Eki. 22.25.\x*, asi itya Mwari wako, kuti umwe wako ararame newe\x + 25.17; Neh. 5.9.\x*.
\v 37 Usamupa mari yako pamubereko, uye usapa kudya kwako pazvibereko\x + 25.42,55; 22.33; 26.13.\x*.
\v 38 Ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu, wakakubudisai munyika yeEgipita, kuti ndikupei nyika yeKenani, ndive Mwari wenyu.
\p
\v 39 Zvino kana umwe wako anewe akava murombo ndokuzvitengesa kwauri, usamushandisa basa renhapwa\x + Eki. 21.2. Det. 15.12. 1 Madz. 9.22. 2 Madz. 4.1. Neh. 5.5. Jer. 34.14.\x*;
\v 40 achava kwauri mushandi wakahaiwa,* semweni; agoshanda newe kusvika gore rejubheri.
\v 41 Ipapo achabuda kwauri, iye nevana vake vanaye\x + Eki. 21.2,3.\x*, agodzokera kurudzi rwake, nekunhaka yemadzibaba ake achadzokera\x + 25.28.\x*.
\v 42 Nokuti varanda vangu vandakabudisa munyika yeEgipita; havangatengeswi \add ne\add*kutengeswa kwenhapwa\x + 25.55. VaRom. 6.22.\x*.
\v 43 Usamutonga nehasha\x + 25.46,53. Eki. 1.13,14. Eze. 34. 4.\x*\x + VaEfe. 6.9. VaKoro. 4.1.\x*, asi utye Mwari wako\x + 25.17. Mara. 3.5.\x*.
\v 44 Zvese nhapwa yako yechirume nenhapwa yako yechikadzi vauchava navo vachava vevechirudzi vanokupoteredzai; kwavari muchatenga nhapwa yechirume nenhapwa yechikadzi.
\v 45 Uyewo pavana vevatorwa vagere sevaeni pakati penyu muchatenga kwavari, nepamhuri dzavo dzinemwi dzevakaberekwa panyika yenyu; uye vachava nhaka yenyu.
\v 46 Zvino muchavatora senhaka yevana venyu vanokuteverai, kuti vagare nhaka\x + Isa. 14.2.\x*; muchavashandisa nekusingaperi; asi pakati pevamwe venyu, vana vaIsraeri, umwe neumwe pamusoro peumwe wake, hamungatongi pamusoro pake nehasha\x + 25.43.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Zvino kana ruoko rwemweni kana mutorwa agere newe rwukasvikira \add pafuma\add*, asi umwe wako anaye akava murombo ndokuzvitengesa kumweni agere newe, kana kunhengo yekudzinza remutorwa uyo\x + 25.25,35,39.\x*,
\v 48 shure kwekuzvitengesa kungava nerudzikunuro rwake; umwe wemadzikoma ake angamudzikunura\x + Neh. 5.1-5.\x*;
\v 49 kana babamunini vake, kana mwanakomana wababamunini vake, angamudzikunura, kana hama yake yepedo yenyama kubva kurudzi rwake angamudzikunura\x + 18.6.\x*; kana ruoko rwake rwukazosvikira, angazvidzikunura\x + 25.26,47.\x*.
\v 50 Zvino achaverengerana newakamutenga kubva gore raakazvitengesa kwaari naro kusvika gore rejubheri, kuti mari yekutengeswa kwake ive seuwandu hwemakore; semazuva emushandi wakahaiwa, zvichadaro kwaari\x + Job. 7.1. Isa. 16.14; 21.16.\x*.
\v 51 Kana pachine makore mazhinji, zvichienderana nawo achadzorera mutengo werudzikunuro rwake kubva pamari yaakatengwa nayo\x + 25.16,52; 27.8.\x*.
\v 52 Zvino kana kwasara makore mashoma kusvika kugore rejubheri, zvino achaverengerana naye; zvichienderana nemakore ake achadzosa mutengo werudzikunuro rwake.
\v 53 Achava naye semushandi wakahaiwa gore negore; haangamutongi nehasha pamberi pemeso ako\x + 25.43.\x*.
\v 54 Zvino kana asina kudzikunurwa neizvi, ipapo achabuda negore rejubheri, iye nevana vake pamwe naye\x + 25.41. Eki. 21.2,3.\x*.
\v 55 Nokuti kwandiri vana vaIsraeri varanda; varanda vangu vandakabudisa kubva munyika yeEgipita\x + 25.42.\x*; ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu.